<html>
  <body
    style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; background-color:#f5f7fb; padding:40px; margin:0;"
  >

    ```
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">

          <table
            width="500"
            style="background:#ffffff; border-radius:10px; padding:30px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);"
          >

            <tr>
              <td align="center">
                <h2 style="margin:0; color:#333;">Payment Reminder</h2>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                style="padding-top:20px; color:#555; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;"
              >
                Your booking is currently
                <strong>waiting for payment</strong>. Please complete your
                payment before the deadline below to keep your reservation.
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding-top:20px;">
                <table
                  width="100%"
                  style="background:#f7f9fc; border-radius:8px; padding:15px;"
                >
                  <tr>
                    <td style="font-size:14px; color:#666;">
                      <strong>Order ID:</strong><br />
                      {{orderId}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding-top:10px; font-size:14px; color:#666;">
                      <strong>Payment Deadline:</strong><br />
                      {{expiredAt}}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td align="center" style="padding-top:25px;">
                <a
                  href="{{paymentLink}}"
                  style="
                background:#4f46e5;
                color:#ffffff;
                text-decoration:none;
                padding:12px 22px;
                border-radius:6px;
                font-size:14px;
                font-weight:bold;
                display:inline-block;
              "
                >
                  Complete Payment
                </a>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                style="padding-top:25px; font-size:12px; color:#999; text-align:center;"
              >
                If you have already completed the payment, you can ignore this
                email.
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>

        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    ```

  </body>
</html>